//www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-An-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-CZX4A7xNs4WPs3fFDSW8Cg">Vương An Quốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/Th%C6%B0-s%C3%A0o-k%C3%BD/poem-so9_x8JRDS-uH2_aEO4INA">Thư sào ký - 書巢記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/Th%C6%B0-t%E1%BA%B7ng-Thi%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%B4-am-Minh-Vi%E1%BB%85n-l%C3%A3o-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/poem-GpbDyGl-byWRGN6lWwhXSA">Thư tặng Thiên Đô am Minh Viễn lão thiền sư - 書贈天都庵明遠老禪師</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/author-il2-xU_Q-nIFla-ypApHCA">Trịnh Hoài Đức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/T%E1%BB%B1-thu%E1%BA%ADt-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-eBpiV8mEO5TqvNOQJYAYBg">Tự thuật kỳ 2 - 自述其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br></div>	</div>
